(By Wu Pin-Chiang)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The rupiah strengthened against the US
dollar Monday and stock prices increased 1 percent following broad
recovery in the region.
</P>
<P>
Dealers and brokers said confidence had gradually returned to the
currency and stock markets following a new freeform package announced
last week.
</P>
