government and businessmen know that they have to unite to succeed,
adding that the Taipei-based International Commercial Bank of China
will send representatives to Central America from time to time to
provide service to Taiwan businessmen.
</P>
<P>
Taiwan businessmen are reluctant to invest in Central America
because of language problems and geographical location. But Kao said
El Salvador has the most solid industrial basis in Central America,
as well as the highest quality of labor.
</P>
<P>
Wang You-cheng, chairman of the Ceneral Chamber of Commerce of
the ROC, quoted Calderon as saying that El Salvador will also provide
assistance to Taiwan businessmen.
</P>
<P>
Wang also suggested that El Salvador sign investment guarantee
agreements with Taiwan and provide incentives for investment to
attract more Taiwan businessmen.
</P>
