</P>
<P>
The bourse opened at 9,070.23 and experienced a high of 9,123.17
and a low of 9,020.37.
</P>
<P>
Gainers outnumbered losers 274 to 120, with 77 remaining
unchanged. In all, 1.37 billion shares changed hands on a market
