meeting on Tuesday with a call for their government leaders to
promote the full participation of women in business and society.
</P>
<P>
The 150-odd woman leaders, including six from the Republic of
China, said APEC leaders can help the fair sex by removing obstacles
they face in entering the business world.
</P>
