(By Ranan Huang and Lilian Wu)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Lien Fang yu, wife of ROC Vice President
Lien Chan, paid a visit to Soong Mayling, widow of former President
Chiang Kai-shek, at her Manhattan residence in New York on Tuesday
afternoon.
</P>
<P>
Mrs. Lien made the visit accompanied by Wu Tzu-dan, director of
