Beijing is seeking a "strategic" relationship with Washington and
that talks on this are continuing.
</P>
<P>
Sheng Guofang, spokesman of mainland China's Foreign Ministry,
observed in response to a CNA reporter's question at a news
conference that Beijing and Washington are discussing the formation
of a kind of strategic partnership that would be an all-around
relationship to include multi-level interaction and dialogue between
