and is preparing a representative office in the Republic of China's
embassy in El Salvador in order to provide more effective loan
services to domestic industrial executives, he noted, adding that the
Ministry of Foreign Affairs will also provide assistance to Taiwan
business people wishing to invest in those two countries, as well as
in Panama and Honduras.
